      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IT'S FRIDAY (1) flew the lids from out wide with a slick early split but ran over at the finish when a narrow fourth (24.84) over 435m at Sale. Should be very hard to beat this time. PAW AMARAN (4) had the drop on the lead and went on to be beaten 1.3 lengths into second (20.13) at this track in a Bottom Up - Grade 5 over 350m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Winning chance. YOU FOUND ME (8) has shown good improvement at her last two starts, finishing in the money last time when 3rd at this track over 350m. Can feature again. PAW INGRID (7) is last start winner who looks one of the chances.",
